snippet: Speaking to a crowd of several hundred Mitt Romney urged voters to come out on caucus night, proclaiming he was going to "win this thing."
abstract: Speaking to a crowd of several hundred Mitt Romney urged voters to come out on caucus night, proclaiming he was going to "win this thing."
lead_paragraph: MARION, Iowa - Mitt Romney told a Cedar Rapids crowd Monday that President Obama is great -- at some things. "I watch a president who's become the great divider, the great complainer, the great excuse-giver, the great blamer," Mr. Romney said.
